      <display_string>[Article] Tangherlini, Timothy R. 1998. "Who ya gonna call?" : Ministers and the Mediation of Ghostly Threat in Danish Legend Tradition. Vol. 57 of &lt;i&gt;Western Folklore&lt;/i&gt; 2/3: 153-178.</display_string>
